title: Mariah Carey Wears Fishnets, Heels At The Gym Because She's Mariah Carey
text:
Mariah Carey Wears Fishnets, Heels At The Gym Because She's Mariah Carey You keep on being you, Mariah. 02/03/2017 11:46 am ET Ron Dicker General Assignment Reporter, The Huffington Post 
Mariah Carey has brought the cabaret to the gym. 
In provocative Instagram images posted Thursday, the singer wore fishnet stockings and stiletto heels to work out. 
While we appreciate that the footwear is the sporting brand Puma (Fenty), we’re still not convinced that this passes muster as training gear. 
But then again, she is Mariah Carey and we’re not. A photo posted by Mariah Carey (@mariahcarey) on Feb 2, 2017 at 7:35pm PST A video posted by Mariah Carey (@mariahcarey) on Feb 2, 2017 at 7:30pm PST A video posted by Mariah Carey (@mariahcarey) on Feb 2, 2017 at 7:18pm PST 
Carey on Thursday also released her new song with rapper YG titled “I Don’t,” which is reportedly inspired by her broken engagement with Australian businessman James Packer. 
Coincidence? Hmm.
